channel.description: Well, recently I've noticed that when Ian NPC attacks me the damage "splat" that tells the amount of damage is not appearing, its very frustrating but I can't find what's wrong. If anyone has had a problem such as this before or anyone knows the coding that makes said splat happen, I would be very thankful if you would post so :), Thanks.
